@startuml
title UC_01 - View Model List

actor User
participant System
database Database

User -> System : Open "Request Device" page
System -> Database : Query model list
Database --> System : Return model data
System -> System : Apply paging
System --> User : Display model list

@enduml


@startuml
title UC_02 - Filter Model

actor User
participant System
database Database

User -> System : Enter filter criteria
System -> Database : Query models with filter
Database --> System : Return filtered data
System --> User : Display filtered list

@enduml

@startuml
title UC_03 - Sort Model

actor User
participant System
database Database

User -> System : Select sort column (ASC/DESC)
System -> Database : Query models with sorting
Database --> System : Return sorted data
System --> User : Display sorted list

@enduml

@startuml
title UC_04 - Borrow Model

actor User
participant System
database Database
participant "Other Instance" as Other

User -> System : Click "Borrow"
activate System

System -> User : Show ContentDialog "Borrow Device"
note right of System
ContentDialog "Borrow Device" gồm:
- Thông tin Model
- Số lượng khả dụng
- ComboBox chọn số lượng
- Nút OK / Cancel
end note

User -> System : Confirm quantity
System -> Database : Check availability
activate Database
Database --> System : Availability result
deactivate Database

alt Available
    System -> Database : Update status to "Occupied"
    activate Database
    Database --> System : Update success
    deactivate Database

    System -> Other : Notify data changed
    System --> User : Show success message
else Not Available
    System --> User : Show error message
end

deactivate System
@enduml


