@startuml
title UC_05 - Return Model

actor User
participant System
database Database
participant "Other Instance" as Other

User -> System : Select devices (checkbox)
activate System

User -> System : Click "Return Selected"

System -> User : Show ContentDialog "Confirm Return"
note right of System
ContentDialog "Confirm Return" gồm:
- Danh sách thiết bị được chọn
- Thông điệp xác nhận
- Nút Confirm / Cancel
end note

User -> System : Confirm return

System -> Database : Update device status
activate Database
Database --> System : Update success
deactivate Database

System -> Other : Notify data changed
System --> User : Show success message

deactivate System
@enduml

@startuml
title UC_06 - Sync Between Instances

participant "System A" as A
database Database
participant "System B" as B

A -> Database : Update device status
activate Database
Database --> A : Update success
deactivate Database

A -> B : Notify data changed

activate B
B -> Database : Reload latest data
activate Database
Database --> B : Return updated data
deactivate Database

B -> B : Refresh UI
deactivate B

@enduml